        <abstract> 
<p>As editor of the new journal, <hi rend="italic">Kosmos</hi>, thanks CD for the permission he has granted Ernst Haeckel to publish with CD’s approval.</p>  
<p>Cites his long support for evolution as exemplified by his book [<hi rend="italic">Die botanische Systematik in ihrem Verhältniss zur Morphologie</hi> (1866)].</p> 
            <p>CD has many German supporters.</p>
        </abstract>
